{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There has been a rift created between realities, and they're calling it &quot;The Schism&quot;. The Schism is a 1-5 player online cooperative horror game, where you and your team of scientists must gather useful intel to aid the governments containment plan. Your team will enter compromised locations, and set about your tasks to collect critical information. But beware, your not alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/extras/Survive_Banner.png?t=1732364356\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Schism features immersive survival mechanics. As your fear increases, an ever growing amount of danger follows in your wake, with immersive hallucinations. Stay alive by keeping calm using a variety of special objects.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Replayability</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Using unpredictable AI, The Schism ensures that each playthrough is unique. This is not a game you play once and throw away. The Schism can offer endless enjoyment with your friends.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Environments</strong><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/extras/Environments_banner.png?t=1732364356\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are highly immersive detailed environments with stunning graphical fidelity. The list of environments you can play in is constantly increasing.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Multiplayer</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Experience the game with up to 4 other friends! Not only will teamwork increase your chances, there is nothing more comical than the hysterics of a friends unfortunate demise. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Plans</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There are massive plans for The Schism. New monsters, maps, and tasks. If you can name it, we've planned it. You can be rest assured, of your investment to this game, as new content will be fundamental. If you have any ideas for new additions however, please reach out in the steam reviews section.</p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1732364356","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1732364356","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1732364356","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1732364356","categories":[{"description":"Multi-player","id":1},{"description":"Co-op","id":9},{"description":"Online Co-op","id":38}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[2,5],"notes":"The game is designed to pursue realism. Players can die in various different ways, and their corpses are visible."},"detailed_description":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">There has been a rift created between realities, and they're calling it &quot;The Schism&quot;. The Schism is a 1-5 player online cooperative horror game, where you and your team of scientists must gather useful intel to aid the governments containment plan. Your team will enter compromised locations, and set about your tasks to collect critical information. But beware, your not alone. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Survival</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2851220/extras/Survive_Ba